name: Blooming
description:
Started nowhere, after a long journey then found a right stop to be grateful of the obstacles and closed doors that led us to the best way. Continuing the journey and blooming in time.

*1,62 tez/1 sold edition will be bought 10 portions of food to donate. Buyer can ask for report by email to bungafatia@rocketmail.com with subject "Warga Bantu Warga".
